13´ë»ó 4:34 Meshobab, Jamlech, Joshah son of Amaziah,
13´ë»ó 4:35 Joel, Jehu son of Joshibiah son of Seraiah son of Asiel,
13´ë»ó 4:36 Elioenai, Jaakobah, Jeshohaiah, Asaiah, Adiel, Jesimiel, Benaiah,
