13´ë»ó 12:5 Eluzai, Jerimoth, Bealiah, Shemariah, Shephatiah the Haruphite;
13´ë»ó 12:6 Elkanah, Isshiah, Azarel, Joezer, and Jashobeam, the Korahites;
